data.description: NEW LISTING ALERT!!!! Don't miss this beautiful home located in the Stone Gate community of McCalla.  This home has had only one owner and has been well-maintained since its construction.  The entire home was repainted in 2022 and features Corian kitchen countertops with built-in stainless steel appliances (stay with home unless buyer does not want them). Gorgeous hardwood floors throughout the main areas and plush carpet in all bedrooms.  Master Bedroom has a jetted tub, stand alone shower and double vanity with huge walk-in closet. The newly remodeled basement is extremely spacious and comes with a fireplace, bedroom, full bath, den equipped for entertaining with surround sound speaker system and dimmer controlled recess lighting.  Owner motivated to sell ASAP!  Don't miss out.  Schedule your appointment TODAY!!!
